data.title: Ohorongo Career Brochure 49f6e61b24
data.meta_description: ohorongo-career-brochure-49f6e61b24 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. Ohorongo Cement offers job attachments and internships to tertiary students from a variety of educational disciplines. Interested students should apply by emailing their CV, tertiary results, cover letter, and internship period details to internship@ohorongo-cement.com. In return, Ohorongo Cement provides real-world work experience and a rewarding environment to help prepare students for future industry careers.
